name: Дятлов 1
description: Extract from the algorithmic music piece: Dyatlov. The piece seeks to reflect the uncertainty and discomfort with which the rescue team found themselves while searching for the lost explorers of the Dyatlov Pass Incident. The images used are photographs recovered from the cameras that belonged to the explorers. The principal audio source is a recorded radio transmission giving the news about this mysterious accident. All the audio was real time processed using SuperCollider, the visuals are real time generated using TouchDesigner
